@startuml
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam defaultFontSize 12

title User Namespaces - Isolation de sécurité (K8s 1.30 Beta)

package "Sans User Namespaces" as without #FFB6C1 {
  rectangle "Container" as c1 {
    component "Process\nUID 0 (root)" as p1 #FF6B6B
  }
  rectangle "Host" as h1 {
    component "Process\nUID 0 (root)" as hp1 #FF6B6B
  }
  c1 -down-> h1 : UID 0 = UID 0\n⚠️ DANGEREUX

  note bottom of h1
    Container escape =
    Accès root sur l'hôte
    CVE-2024-21626
  end note
}

package "Avec User Namespaces" as with #90EE90 {
  rectangle "Container" as c2 {
    component "Process\nUID 0 (root)" as p2 #FFD700
  }
  rectangle "Host" as h2 {
    component "Process\nUID 65534 (nobody)" as hp2 #90EE90
  }
  c2 -down-> h2 : UID 0 → UID 65534\n✅ SÉCURISÉ

  note bottom of h2
    Container escape =
    Utilisateur non privilégié
    Impact limité
  end note
}

note bottom
  **Configuration Pod:**
  ```yaml
  spec:
    hostUsers: false  # Active user namespaces
    containers:
    - name: app
      securityContext:
        runAsUser: 0  # root DANS le container
  ```

  **Mapping réel:**
  Container UID 0    → Host UID 65534
  Container UID 1000 → Host UID 66534
end note

legend right
  |= Mode |= Risque |
  | hostUsers: true | Élevé (défaut) |
  | hostUsers: false | Faible ✅ |
endlegend

@enduml
